title: Shazam: Fury of the Gods - The Sequel No One Wanted
description:
So Shazam 2 is upon us and... well, it hasn't exactly gone down a storm. Join me for this review of the sequel nobody wanted or asked for. 

Link to my Rambo comic: https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/first-kill-graphic-novel#/

title: Open Bar #42 - Victoria Alonso Fired, Disney Chaos, Lucasfilm In Panic, Shazam 2 Bombs
description:
The bar is open! Join me, MauLer, Nerdrotic, Midnight's Edge and Chris Gore as we discuss the firing of Marvel head honcho Victoria Alonso, what it means for Disney, the legal problems of Lucasfilm, and the disaster of Shazam 2.
